snippet.title: Deadlink - Official Full Release Date Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description:
The full release of Deadlink will be available on PC on July 27, 2023. Watch the latest action-packed trailer for another look at this cyberpunk FPS with roguelite elements. In Deadlink, your mission is to conduct covert ops while piloting a humanoid combat shell. And no, "covert" doesn’t mean "quiet."

#IGN #SoG
